title: The Mysterious City Golden Prague (hidden object)
description:
Explorer the beautiful and historic city of Prague as you search for clues in the disappearance of Professor Goldy.
Your peaceful morning is interrupted by a frantic knock on your door. Your beloved professor has gone missing from the museum where he was last seen. With only a week until the magnificent golden clock is scheduled to open, it&#039;s up to you to explore the beautiful and historic city of Prague; from the intriguing museums and mysterious castles to its mysterious underbelly. Discover the clues the professor left, and piece together what happened before it&#039;s too late!
